<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en-US">

<head>
  <title>Insights Demo</title>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <meta name="ct" content="<%= ct %>">
  <link rel="shortcut icon" href="/images/favicon.ico" type="image/x-icon">
  <link rel="icon" href="/images/favicon.ico" type="image/x-icon">
  <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/css/style.css">
  <script type="text/javascript" src="https://www.google.com/recaptcha/api.js"></script>
</head>

<body>

  <div class="init-text">
    <h1>IBM Bluemix</h1>
    <h3>Personality Insights &amp; Insights for Twitter</h3>
    <hr>
    <p>This application delivers a simple analysis of your personality given your twitts (based on your own and also your @ mentions in twitter), 
    we take the top most and the lowest most personality characteristics and deliver a description based on them. The idea behind this is to “help” a finance institution representative to make decisions about your qualifications, in terms of personality, to be eligible for a loan.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-12 col-xs-12">
        <div class="well">
          <div class="form-group row">
            <div style="padding:0px;" class="col-lg-12 col-xs-12">
              <label class="col-lg-6 col-md-6 col-xs-6 control-label">Please Choose Language (language in which you twitt most):</label>
              <br><br>
              <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-6 col-xs-6 sample-radio-list">
                <div class="sample-radio-container">
                  <label>
                    <input id="english_radio" type="radio" name="sample_text" value="en" checked class="sample-radio">
                    <span>English</span>
                  </label>
                </div>
                <div class="sample-radio-container">
                  <label>
                    <input type="radio" name="sample_text" value="es" class="sample-radio">
                    <span>Spanish</span>
                  </label>
                </div>
              </div>
              <textarea rows="1" required="true" name="text" class="content form-control"></textarea>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="form-group row buttons-container">
            <div class="col-lg-4 col-xs-4">
              <button type="button" class="btn btn-block clear-btn">Clear</button>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-4 col-lg-push-4 col-xs-4 col-xs-push-4">
              <button type="button" class="btn btn-block analysis-btn">Analyze</button>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
   
      </div>

      <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-12 col-xs-12">
        <div style="display:none;" class="form-group row loading text-center loading">
          <h2>&nbsp;</h2>
          <img src="images/watson.gif">
        </div>
        <div style="display: none;" class="form-group row error">
          <h2>&nbsp;</h2>
          <div class="well">
            <p class="errorMsg"></p>
            <div style="display:none;margin-bottom:10px;" class="captcha">
              <div data-sitekey="6LcRbQkTAAAAAGUFVbnuqDfse-XZASLZwoC34oJV" class="g-recaptcha"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

          <div style="display: none;" class="results">
          <h2>Your Personality</h2>
          <div class="well">
            <div class="summary-div"></div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>

      <div style="display: none;" class="results">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-lg-5 col-md-12 col-xs-12">

            <h3>Data Behind Your Personality</h3>
            
            <div class="others">
              <h4>How Others see you</h4>
              <div style="display: none;" class="col555px well traits"></div>
              <div style="display: none;" class="col555px well badtraits"></div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="self">
              <h4>This is based in your own content</h4>
              <div style="display: none;" class="col555px well self-traits"></div>
              <div style="display: none;" class="col555px well self-badtraits"></div>
            </div>
              
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>

      
      <div class="hidden">  
      
        <div id="trait-template">
          <div class="row">
            <div class="tname col-lg-7 col-xs-7">
              <span></span>
            </div>
            <div class="tvalue col-lg-5 col-xs-5 text-right">
              <span></span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div id="self-trait-template">
          <div class="row">
            <div class="tname col-lg-7 col-xs-7">
              <span></span>
            </div>
            <div class="tvalue col-lg-5 col-xs-5 text-right">
              <span></span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <script type="text/javascript" src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-1.11.3.min.js"></script>
  <script type="text/javascript" src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/d3/2.10.0/d3.v2.min.js"></script>
  <script type="text/javascript" src="/js/demo.js"></script>
  <script type="text/javascript" src="/js/personality.js"></script>
  <script type="text/javascript" src="/js/string-utils.js"></script>
  <script type="text/javascript" src="/js/i18n.js"></script>
  <script type="text/javascript" src="/js/textsummary.js"></script>
  <script type="text/javascript">
    textSummary.init('json');
  </script>
</body>

</html>
